ned it.', 614, 0), (58838, 'I am a Jew. Hath not a Jew eyes? Hath not a Jew hands, organs, dimensions, senses, affections, passions; fed with the same food, hurt with the same weapons, subject to the same diseases, heal''d by the same means, warm''d and cool''d by the same winter and summer, as a Christian is? If you prick us, do we not bleed? If you tickle us, do we not laugh? If you poison us, do we not die? And if you wrong us, do we not revenge? If we are like you in the rest, we will resemble you in that.', 13, 0), (58839, 'Cultivate your curves - they may be dangerous but they won''t be avoided.', 978, 0), (58840, 'Other crack teams get bat boomerangs and wall-climbing powers we get Aquatruck. ', 39, 0), (58841, 'We were kissing.I thought: This is good.I thought: I am not bad at this kissing. Not bad at all.I thought: I am clearly the greatest kisser in the history of the universe.Suddenly she laughed and pulled away from me. She wiggled a hand out of her sleeping bag and wiped her face. "You slobbered on my nose," she said, and laughed', 9, 0), (58842, 'Adrian, I''m on a date. Why are you here? On my car?', 83, 0), (58843, 'How long have you been standing there?""Just long enough to see you give Daemon the middle finger.""He deserved it.', 366, 0), (58844, 'I''ve been to Canada, and I''ve always gotten the impression that I could take the country over in about two days.', 2197, 0), (58845, 'Anyone who says he can see through women is missing a lot.', 1040, 0), (58846, 'Scoot over, man. I don''t like you that much." "Dick. That''s not what you said last night.""Bite me.', 614, 0), (58847, 'Your mail could''ve waited." Daemon followed me into the kitchen. "What is it? Just books?"Grabbing the OJ from the fridge, I sighed. People who didn''t heart books didn''t understand.', 366, 0), (58848, 'A real girl isn''t perfect and a perfect girl isn''t real.', 500, 0), (58849, 'Whoa, who peed in your Cheerios?', 155, 0), (58850, 'She didn''t care that people called her 